These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, mystery
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | tea  | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | musical   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour |
| Transport     | subway | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, asparagus
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, zombie
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, boat
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | kale     | asparagus |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | animation  |
| Pet           | goldfish         | ferret     |
| Transport     | helicopter   | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, manager
2 different pets are kept: dog, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the manager##3
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | sprite     | cola |
| Job         | manager | analyst    |
| Pet         | dog         | pony        |
| Transport   | train         | van    |

