There 2 different types of food: apple, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, camping
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, house
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea     | milk |
| Food          | spinach   | apple  |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping     |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | house         |

