.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, scientist
There are 2 different nationalities: american, argentine
2 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
2. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
3. the scientist is the american##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | scientist | photographer    |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine |
| Pet           | ferret         | guinea-pig    |
| Sport         | basketball    | rowing   |

